'''Aaron McClellan''' (born [[February 8]], [[1950s#1959|1959]]) is an artist who illustrated one of the ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]'' supplements. Along with [[Michael Manley]] and [[Al Williamson]], he provided the sketches for ''[[Tales from the Mos Eisley Cantina]]'' and ''[[Tales from Jabba's Palace]]''.

